<title>SOUTH KOREA: TABLE-Hanwha Corp first-half net rises.</title>
<headline>TABLE-Hanwha Corp first-half net rises.</headline>
<dateline>SEOUL 1997-08-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to June 30</p>
<p>		 (in billion won unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (won)		   295	vs	  199</p>
<p>    Net			  9.10	vs	 5.03</p>
<p>    Turnover	     1,217.33	vs     778.65</p>
<p>    Profit before tax     10.82	vs	 6.35</p>
<p>Note - Hanwha Corp is an affiliate of the Hanwha Group. The Korea Listed Companies Association provided the figures but gave no further details.</p>
